CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, July 28, 1962, pg. 22, reads: "Guests At Soiree - Among the out-of-town guests who enjoyed the Junior Mothers' week-end was this group, which includes former Pittsburghers. Pictured at the JM's soiree Friday night at the Hotel Roosevelt are (left to right) Mrs. Wilson Primas and Wilson Primas, Harrisburg, Pa.; Mrs. June Tansimore Ross, Newport News, Va.; Mrs. and Mrs. George Gibson, Bronx, N.Y., and Miss Nancy Reynolds, Columbus, Ohio.  The Primases, Mrs. Ross and Mrs. Gibson are ex-Pittsburghers. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Group portrait, from left: Mrs. Primas, Wilson Primas, June Tansimore Ross, George Gibson, Mrs. Gibson, and Nancy Reynolds, standing at base of staircase in Roosevelt Hotel for Junior Mothers party
